    {
      "type": "content",
      "content": {
        "title": {
          "english": "Finishing Work or School"
        },
        "text": "To express that you 'finish work' or 'finish school', you use the verb بخلّص (bkḫallis - I finish).",
        "examples": [
          {
            "arabic": "أنا بخلّص شغل الساعة خمسة.",
            "english": "I finish work at 5 o'clock.",
            "transliteration": "Ana bkḫallis shughl is-saa'a khamse."
          },
          {
            "arabic": "هي بتخلّص مدرسة الظهر.",
            "english": "She finishes school at noon.",
            "transliteration": "Hiyye btkḫallis madrasa iḍ-ḍuhr."
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "content",
      "content": {
        "title": {
          "english": "Coming Home"
        },
        "text": "To say 'I return home' or 'I come home', use the verb برجع (barja' - I return) with عالبيت (a'l-bait - to home).",
        "examples": [
          {
            "arabic": "أنا برجع عالبيت بعد الشغل.",
            "english": "I return home after work.",
            "transliteration": "Ana barja' a'l-bait ba'd ish-shughl."
          },
          {
            "arabic": "هو بيرجع عالبيت المسا.",
            "english": "He returns home in the evening.",
            "transliteration": "Huwa beerja' a'l-bait il-masa."
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "content",
      "content": {
        "title": {
          "english": "Relaxing and Watching TV"
        },
        "text": "To talk about relaxing, use برتاح (bartaḥ - I relax). For watching TV, use بحضر تلفزيون (baḥḍar tilifizyoun - I watch TV).",
        "examples": [
          {
            "arabic": "أنا برتاح شوي قبل العشا.",
            "english": "I relax a bit before dinner.",
            "transliteration": "Ana bartaḥ shway qabl il-'asha."
          },
          {
            "arabic": "هي بتحضر تلفزيون بالليل.",
            "english": "She watches TV at night.",
            "transliteration": "Hiyye btaḥḍar tilifizyoun bil-lail."
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "practice-sentence",
      "sentence": {
        "arabic": "أنا بخلّص شغل وبرجع عالبيت.",
        "english": "I finish work and return home.",
